      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUMMER MOUSE (1) is better than last start when seventh (22.77) from Box 2 at Q Lakeside over 390m. The form out of her last race has been franked. Has claims if she runs up to expectations. ALIIR (4) placed last time (30.05) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing second and beaten 1.5 lengths. Has already won four times from this draw. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. SHE'S OUR GAL (2) has some solid form under her belt and proved too classy last time to win by 3.5 lengths at Q Lakeside in a handy 25.69 beating Weblec Jewel. Will go close again if runs up to latest. RIORSON BALE (7) profiles nicely here at this trip.",
